ei','Shipping method' => 'Shipping metoade','Additional notes' => 'Oanfoljende notysjes','Billing to' => 'Billing oan','Payment method' => 'Payment metoade','Step %1$s of %2$s' => 'Stap %1$s fan %2$s','Change: %s' => 'Feroarje: %s','Not selected yet.' => 'Noch net selektearre.','Same as shipping address' => 'Itselde as ferstjoeradres','Same as billing address' => 'Itselde as fakturearring adres','Order summary' => 'Order gearfetting','Edit cart' => 'Cart bewurkje','Did you mean %s?' => 'Bedoelde jo %s?','Change email address to: {suggestion-value}' => 'E-postadres feroarje yn: {suggestion-value}','This is a required field.' => 'Dit is in fereaske fjild.','This is not a valid email address.' => 'Dit is gjin jildich e-mailadres.','This field does not match the related field value.' => 'Dit fjild komt net oerien mei de relatearre fjildwearde.','The CPF number "{cpf_number}" is invalid.' => 'It CPF-nûmer &quot;{cpf_number}&quot; is ûnjildich.','The CNPJ number "{cnpj_number}" is invalid.' => 'It CNPJ-nûmer &quot;{cnpj_number}&quot; is ûnjildich.','(Required)' => '(ferplicht)','Checkout Header - Desktop' => 'Checkout Header - Buroblêd','Display widgets on the checkout header for large screens. Only displayed if using the plugin\'s checkout header.' => 'Toan widgets op &#39;e kop fan&#39; e kassa foar grutte skermen. Allinnich werjûn as jo de koptekst fan &#39;e checkout fan&#39; e plugin brûke.','Checkout Header - Mobile' => 'Checkout Header - Mobyl','Display widgets below the checkout header for mobile devices. Only displayed if using the plugin\'s checkout header.' => 'Toan widgets ûnder de kassakoptekst foar mobile apparaten. Allinnich werjûn as jo de koptekst fan &#39;e checkout fan&#39; e plugin brûke.','Checkout Sidebar' => 'Checkout Sidebar','Display widgets on the checkout sidebar after the order summary.' => 'Toan widgets op &#39;e sydbalke fan&#39; e kassa nei de gearfetting fan &#39;e bestelling.','Checkout Order Summary' => 'Checkout Order Gearfetting','Display widgets inside the order summary at the checkout page.' => 'Toan widgets binnen de oarder gearfetting by de kassa side.','Checkout Below Place Order' => 'Checkout hjirûnder pleatse oarder','Display widgets below the place order button at the checkout page.' => 'Toan widgets ûnder de plak bestelling knop by de kassa side.','Checkout Footer' => 'Checkout Footer','Display widgets on the checkout footer. Only displayed if using the plugin\'s checkout footer.' => 'Widgets werjaan op &#39;e fuottekst fan&#39; e kassa. Allinnich werjûn as jo de fuottekst fan &#39;e checkout fan&#39; e plugin brûke.','Classic' => 'Klassyk','Boxed' => 'Boxed','Split' => 'Spjalte','Minimalist' => 'Minimalistysk','Fluid Checkout and Delivery Date plugins by CodeRockz' => 'Fluid Checkout en Delivery Date plugins troch CodeRockz','<p>We detected that you are using the plugins Delivery & Pickup Date Time for WooCommerce (free and PRO) by CodeRockz. Integration with these plugins have been moved to Fluid Checkout PRO.</p>' => '<p>Wy ûntdutsen dat jo de plugins brûke Delivery &amp; Pickup Date Time foar WooCommerce (fergees en PRO) troch CodeRockz. Yntegraasje mei dizze plugins binne ferpleatst nei Fluid Checkout PRO.</p>','Upgrade to PRO' => 'Upgrade nei PRO','Fluid Checkout database updated successfully' => 'Fluid Checkout-database mei súkses bywurke','The database changes where applied successfully.' => 'De databank feroaret wêr&#39;t mei súkses tapast.','Ok' => 'Ok','Dismiss' => 'ôfwize','Fluid Checkout database update' => 'Fluid Checkout databank update','Some changes to the database are required. As with any update, we recommend you to <strong>take a full backup of your website before proceeding</strong>.' => 'Guon wizigingen oan de databank binne nedich. Lykas by elke fernijing, riede wy jo oan om <strong>in folsleine reservekopy fan jo webside te nimmen foardat jo trochgean</strong> .','Update database' => 'Update databank','Fluid Checkout is not compatible with the Divi Builder checkout layout' => 'Fluid Checkout is net kompatibel mei de Divi Builder kassa-yndieling','<p>Fluid Checkout needs the classic WooCommerce shortcode-based checkout form to work. When using the Divi Builder to customize the look and feel of the checkout page, the classic shortcodes are replaced with custom widgets from the Divi Builder for each part of the checkout page. These custom widgets are not compatible with Fluid Checkout.</p><p>Please edit your checkout page replacing the Divi Builder widgets with the a text widget containing the shortcode <code>[woocommerce_checkout]</code>.</p>' => '<p>Fluid Checkout hat it klassike WooCommerce shortcode-basearre kassaformulier nedich om te wurkjen. By it brûken fan de Divi Builder om it uterlik en gefoel fan &#39;e kassaside oan te passen, wurde de klassike koartekoades ferfongen troch oanpaste widgets fan&#39; e Divi Builder foar elk diel fan &#39;e kassaside. Dizze oanpaste widgets binne net kompatibel mei Fluid Checkout.</p><p> Bewurkje asjebleaft jo kassaside troch de Divi Builder-widgets te ferfangen troch in tekstwidget mei de koarte koade <code>[woocommerce_checkout]</code> .</p>','Edit the checkout page' => 'Bewurkje de kassa side','Read the documentation.' => 'Lês de dokumintaasje.','Germanized PRO multistep checkout feature needs to be disabled when using Fluid Checkout' => 'Germanized PRO multistep checkout-funksje moat wurde útskeakele by it brûken fan Fluid Checkout','When using Fluid Checkout, the multistep feature from the Germanized PRO plugin becomes unnecessary and can cause <strong>critical errors while processing new orders</strong>. Please disable the Germanized PRO multistep checkout feature in the plugin settings.' => 'By it brûken fan Fluid Checkout, wurdt de multistep-funksje fan &#39;e germanisearre PRO-plugin net nedich en kin <strong>krityske flaters feroarsaakje by it ferwurkjen fan nije oarders</strong> . Skeakelje asjebleaft de Germanized PRO multistep checkout-funksje út yn &#39;e plugin-ynstellingen.','Go to Germanized settings' => 'Gean nei germanisearre ynstellings','Thanks for choosing Fluid Checkout!' => 'Betanke foar it kiezen fan Fluid Checkout!','You have been using the plugin for a while now. How do you like it so far? <br>Please give us a quick rating, we appreciate every bit of feedback and it encourages us to keep improving the plugin :)' => 'Jo hawwe de plugin al in skoft brûkt. Hoe fynst it oant no ta?<br> Jou ús asjebleaft in rappe wurdearring, wy wurdearje elke feedback en it stimulearret ús om de plugin te ferbetterjen :)','Rate the plugin' => 'Beoardielje de plugin','I need help!' => 'Ik haw help nedich!','Some features of WooCommerce Checkout Manager by Quadlayers might not work as expected when using it with Fluid Checkout. Read <a href="%s">our documentation</a> for more information and alternative solutions.' => 'Guon funksjes fan WooCommerce Checkout Manager troch Quadlayers wurkje miskien net lykas ferwachte by it brûken fan it mei Fluid Checkout. Lês <a href="%s">ús dokumintaasje</a> foar mear ynformaasje en alternative oplossings.','Read documentation' => 'Lês dokumintaasje','Don\'t show this again' => 'Lit dit net wer sjen','Special offers' => 'Spesjale oanbiedingen','Extend all the goodness of Fluid Checkout to your cart page and thank you pages.' => 'Wreidzje alle goedens fan Fluid Checkout út nei jo karreside en tankje siden.','Fluid Checkout PRO' => 'Fluid Checkout PRO','Design templates, optimized cart and order received pages, account matching, and much more.' => 'Untwerpsjabloanen, optimalisearre karre en bestelle ûntfongen siden, oerienkommende akkounts, en folle mear.','The best tools to further <strong>improve your WooCommerce checkout conversion rate</strong> and make the purchase experience consistent on the entire journey.' => 'De bêste ark om <strong>jo WooCommerce-konverzje-konversaasjerate fierder te ferbetterjen</strong> en de oankeapûnderfining konsekwint te meitsjen op &#39;e heule reis.','More design templates' 