wn on the website superseed these and will be applied.' => 'Alle prizen werjûn yn EUR. As d&#39;r ferskillen binne mei de prizen op ús webside, sille de oanbiedingen werjûn op &#39;e webside dizze ferfange en wurde tapast.','Add-ons' => 'Add-ons','Enhance your checkout experience with these add-ons.' => 'Ferbetterje jo kassaûnderfining mei dizze tafoegings.','I already have it – Hide this offer' => 'Ik haw it al - Ferbergje dit oanbod','Installed &mdash; Activate' => 'Ynstallearre - Aktivearje','Activated' => 'Aktivearre','Up to 40% less checkout fields to fill in.' => 'Oant 40% minder kassafjilden om yn te foljen.','Avoid delivery delays and unsatisfied customers. Collect the <strong>correct address information</strong> from the first time they buy with you.' => 'Foarkom levering fertragingen en ûntefreden klanten. Sammelje de <strong>juste adresynformaasje</strong> fan &#39;e earste kear dat se mei jo keapje.','Get this add-on &mdash; 29 EUR' => 'Krij dizze tafoeging - 29 EUR','Address book' => 'Adresboek','Multiple saved addresses for shipping and billing.' => 'Meardere bewarre adressen foar ferstjoering en fakturearring.','Let customers <strong>save multiple shipping and billing addresses</strong> on their account and choose which ones to use at checkout and cart pages.' => 'Lit klanten <strong>meardere ferstjoerings- en fakturearadressen op har akkount bewarje</strong> en kieze hokker te brûken by kassa- en karresiden.','Get this add-on &mdash; 59 EUR' => 'Krij dizze tafoeging - 59 EUR','Simplified EU-VAT validation for your store.' => 'Ienfâldige EU-BTW-validaasje foar jo winkel.','Collect and <strong>validate EU VAT numbers at the checkout page</strong>, removes tax charges on reverse charge basis and confirms customer location when needed.' => 'Sammelje en <strong>falidearje EU-btw-nûmers op &#39;e kassaside</strong> , ferwideret belestingskosten op basis fan omkearde lading en befêstiget klantlokaasje as it nedich is.','Get this add-on &mdash; 39 EUR' => 'Krij dizze tafoeging - 39 EUR','All add-ons are sold separately and require the <strong>Fluid Checkout Lite</strong> plugin to be installed and activated, except when noted.' => 'Alle tafoegings wurde apart ferkocht en fereaskje dat de <strong>Fluid Checkout Lite-</strong> plugin wurdt ynstalleare en aktivearre, útsein as opmurken.','Select an image' => 'Selektearje in ôfbylding','<a href="https://fluidcheckout.com/account/" target="_blank">Log in to your account</a> to get your license key, or <a href="%s" target="_blank">purchase a new license key</a>.' => '<a href="https://fluidcheckout.com/account/" target="_blank">Meld jo oan by jo akkount</a> om jo lisinsjekaai te krijen, of <a href="%s" target="_blank">keapje in nije lisinsjekaai</a> .','Valid until %s.' => 'Jildich oant %s.','Expired on %s.' => 'Ferrûn op %s.','<a href="https://fluidcheckout.com/account/" target="_blank">Log in to your account</a> to renew your license key and continue to receive updates and support.' => '<a href="https://fluidcheckout.com/account/" target="_blank">Meld jo oan by jo akkount</a> om jo lisinsjekaai te fernijen en trochgean mei updates en stipe te ûntfangen.','License key cancelled.' => 'Lisinsjekaai annulearre.','<a href="%s" target="_blank">Purchase a new license key</a> and continue to receive updates and support.' => '<a href="%s" target="_blank">Keapje in nije lisinsjekaai</a> en trochgean mei updates en stipe te ûntfangen.','Error: ' => 'Fersin: ','Setup & Documentation' => 'Ynstelling &amp; dokumintaasje','Great! Your checkout page is now running on Fluid Checkout.' => 'Grut! Jo kassaside rint no op Fluid Checkout.','Here are a few resources for you to get started:' => 'Hjir binne in pear boarnen foar jo om te begjinnen:','Read the installation guide <a href="%s" target="_blank">Getting stated with Fluid Checkout</a>.' => 'Lês de ynstallaasjegids <a href="%s" target="_blank">Getting stated mei Fluid Checkout</a> .','Setup layout and design on the <a href="%s">checkout options</a>.' => 'Yndieling en ûntwerp ynstelle op &#39;e <a href="%s">kassa-opsjes</a> .','Check if there are any <a href="%s">integration options</a> available for other plugins you have installed.' => 'Kontrolearje oft d&#39;r <a href="%s">yntegraasjeopsjes</a> beskikber binne foar oare plugins dy&#39;t jo ynstalleare hawwe.','Visit <a href="%s" target="_blank">our documentation</a> for more information about Fluid Checkout features.' => 'Besykje <a href="%s" target="_blank">ús dokumintaasje</a> foar mear ynformaasje oer Fluid Checkout-funksjes.','If you ever need help, <a href="%s" target="_blank">open a support ticket</a> on our official support channel.' => 'As jo oait help nedich hawwe, <a href="%s" target="_blank">iepenje dan in stipekaart</a> op ús offisjele stipekanaal.','Cart layout' => 'Cart yndieling','Cart optimizations' => 'Cart optimizations','Enable cart page optimizations' => 'Aktivearje cart side-optimisaasjes','Display the cart page with a layout similar to the checkout page.' => 'Lit de karreside sjen mei in yndieling fergelykber mei de kassaside.','Header and footer' => 'Kop- en fuottekst','Header and footer template' => 'Sjabloan foar koptekst en fuottekst','Controls whether to use the distraction free page header and footer or keep the currently active theme\'s header and footer.' => 'Kontrolearret of de kop- en fuottekst fan &#39;e pagina sûnder ôflieding brûkt wurdt of de kop- en fuottekst fan it op it stuit aktive tema te hâlden.','Distraction free header and footer' => 'Kop- en fuottekst sûnder ôflieding','Theme\'s header and footer' => 'De kop- en fuottekst fan it tema','Cart elements' => 'Cart eleminten','Make the order summary stay visible on the cart page while scrolling' => 'Meitsje de gearfetting fan &#39;e bestelling sichtber te bliuwen op&#39; e karreside by it rôljen','Coupon codes' => 'Coupon koades','Select position where to display the coupon codes section on the cart page. Only applicable when AJAX cart and the integrated coupon codes in the checkout page are enabled.' => 'Selektearje posysje wêr&#39;t de seksje fan couponkoades op &#39;e cart-side te werjaan. Allinnich fan tapassing as AJAX-karre en de yntegreare kûponkoades yn &#39;e kassaside binne ynskeakele.','Hidden' => 'Ferburgen','Before the cart items section' => 'Foardat de seksje fan karre items','Inside the cart items section' => 'Binnen de seksje fan karre items','After the cart items section' => 'Nei de karre items seksje','Before the shipping section' => 'Foardat de skipfeart seksje','After the shipping section' => 'Nei de skipfeart seksje','Before the order summary' => 'Foardat de oarder gearfetting','Inside the order summary' => 'Binnen de oarder gearfetting','Before the order totals' => 'Foardat de oarder totalen','After the order totals' => 'Nei de oarder totalen','After the order summary' => 'Nei de oarder gearfetting','Shipping' => 'Skipfeart','Select position where to display the shipping costs and calculator on the cart page.' => 'Selektearje posysje wêr&#39;t jo de ferstjoerkosten en rekkenmasine werjaan op &#39;e karre side.','Display as a cart section' => 'Werjaan as in karre seksje','Cross-sells' => 'Cross-sells','Select position where to display the cross-sells section on the cart page.' => 'Selektearje posysje wêr&#39;t de seksje fan cross-sells op &#39;e karreside werjûn wurde sil.','Before the cart actions' => 'Foardat de karre aksjes','After the cart actions' => 'Nei de karre aksjes','Layout of cross-sell items on the cart page.' => 'Opmaak fan cross-sell items op de cart side.','Optimized horizontal cross-sells layout' => 'Optimalisearre horizontale cross-sells yndieling','Theme\'s cross-sells layout' => 'Tema&#39;s cross-sell-yndieling','Number of cross-sell items to display on the cart page' => 'Oantal cross-sell-items om te werjaan op &#39;e cart-side','Trust symbols &amp; badges' => 'Trust symboalen &amp; badges','Add widget areas to the cart page' => 'Foegje widgetgebieten ta oan &#39;e karreside','These widget areas are used to add trust symbols and trust badges on the cart page.' => 'Dizze widgetgebieten wurde brûkt om fertrouwensymboalen en fertrouwensbadges ta te foegjen op &#39;e karreside.','Checkout' => 'Betelje','Layout &amp; design' => 'Layout &amp; ûntwerp','Checkout layout' => 'Checkout yndieling','Design template' => 'Design sjabloan','General styles for the checkout steps, order summary and other sections. Might also apply to other pages such as the Cart, Order Received and View Order pages.' => 'Algemiene stilen foar de kassa stappen, oarder gearfetting en oare seksjes. Kin ek jilde foar oare siden lykas de Cart, Order Received en View Order siden.','Dark mode' => 'Tsjustere modus','Enable dark mode' => 'Tsjustere modus ynskeakelje','Header and footer templates' => 'Sjabloanen foar koptekst en fuottekst','We recommend using the distraction free header and footer to avoid distractions at the checkout page. <a href="https://baymard.com/blog/cart-abandonment" target="_blank">Read the research about cart abandonment</a>.' => 'Wy riede oan om de ôfliedingsfrije kop- en fuottekst te brûken om ôfliedingen by de kassaside te foarkommen. <a href="https://baymard.com/blog/cart-abandonment" target="_blank">Lês it ûndersyk oer it ferlitten fan karre</a> .','Logo image' => 'Logo ôfbylding','Choose an image to be displayed on the checkout page header. Only applies when using the distraction free header and footer.' => 'Kies in ôfbylding om te werjaan op &#39;e kop fan&#39; e kassapagina. Allinnich jildt by it brûken fan de ôfliedingsfrije kop- en fuottekst.','Header background color' => 'Koptekst eftergrûnkleur','Choose a background color for the checkout page header. Only applies when using the distraction free header and footer.' => 'Kies in eftergrûnkleur foar de koptekst fan de kassapagina. Allinnich jildt by it brûken fan de ôfliedingsfrije kop- en fuottekst.','HTML color value. ie: #f3f3f3' => 'HTML kleur wearde. ie: #f3f3f3','Page background color' => 'Side eftergrûn kleur','Choose a background color for the checkout page. Color is applied to the <em>body</em> element.' => 'Kies in eftergrûnkleur foar de kassaside. Kleur wurdt tapast op it <em>lichem</em> elemint.','Footer background color' => 'Fuottekst eftergrûnkleur','Choose a background color for the checkout page footer. Only applies when using the distraction free header and footer.' => 'Kies in eftergrûnkleur foar de fuottekst fan de kassapagina. Allinnich jildt by it brûken fan de ôfliedingsfrije kop- en fuottekst.','Checkout elements' => 'Checkout eleminten','Progress bar' => 'Progress bar','Display the checkout progress bar when using multi-step checkout layout' => 'Lit de foarútgongsbalke fan &#39;e kassa werjaan by it brûken fan multi-stap checkout-yndieling','Make the checkout progress bar stay visible while scrolling' => 'Lit de foarútgongsbalke fan &#39;e kassa sichtber bliuwe by it rôljen','Express checkout' => 'Express checkout','Enable the express checkout section' => 'Skeakelje de seksje foar ekspresje ôfrekkenje','Displays the express checkout section at checkout when supported payment gateways have this feature enabled.' => 'Toant de seksje foar ekspresje ôfrekken by it ôfrekkenjen as stipe foar betellingspoarten dizze funksje ynskeakele hawwe.','Display express checkout buttons in one line for larger screens' => 'Werjaan express kassa knoppen yn ien rigel foar gruttere skermen','Ignore additional checkout required fields when paying with a compatible express checkout payment gateway' => 'Negearje oanfoljende kassa fereaske fjilden by it beteljen mei in kompatible express checkout betelling gateway','Make the order summary stay visible while scrolling' => 'Meitsje de oarder gearfetting bliuwe sichtber wylst scrollen','Choose a background color for the order summary section.' => 'Kies in eftergrûnkleur foar de seksje foar gearfetting fan &#39;e bestelling.','Highlight the order totals row in the order summary table' => 'Markearje de oarder totalen rige yn de oarder gearfetting tabel','Most useful when the order summary section does not have a highlighted background color. Might also apply to the Cart, Order Received and View Order pages when using Fluid Checkout PRO.' => 'Meast nuttich as de seksje foar gearfetting fan &#39;e bestelling gjin markearre eftergrûnkleur hat. Kin ek jilde foar de Cart, Order Untfongen en View Order siden by it brûken fan Fluid Checkout PRO.','Action link on the order summary at checkout.' => 'Aksje keppeling op de oarder gearfetting by kassa.','Edit cart link' => 'Cart link bewurkje','Cart items count' => 'Cart items telle','Link to shop page' => 'Link nei winkel side','Cart items' => 'Cart items','Enable options to edit cart items on the checkout page' => 'Opsjes ynskeakelje om karre items op &#39;e kassaside te bewurkjen','Allow customers to change product quantities or removing items directly at the checkout page.' => 'Tastean klanten te feroarjen produkt hoemannichten of fuortsmite items direkt by de kassa side.','Hide cart items errors at the checkout page' => 'Ferbergje cart items flaters by de kassa side','Do not display the cart items errors message at the top of the checkout page. When submitting the checkout form to complete the purchase, these error messages will always be displayed.' => 'Net werjaan de cart items flaters berjocht oan de boppekant fan de kassa side. By it yntsjinjen fan it kassaformulier om de oankeap te foltôgjen, sille dizze flaterberjochten altyd werjûn wurde.','Place order' => 'Plak oarder','Define the position to display "Place order" and terms checkbox section.' => 'Definiearje de posysje om &quot;Bestelling pleatse&quot; en betingsten karfakje seksje te werjaan.','Some options might not be compatible with some plugins and themes.' => 'Guon opsjes binne miskien net kompatibel mei guon plugins en tema&#39;s.','Below the payment section' => 'Under de betelling seksje','Below the order summary' => 'Under de oarder gearfetting','Both below the payment section and the order summary' => 'Sawol ûnder de betelling seksje as de oarder gearfetting','Add widget areas to the checkout page' => 'Foegje widgetgebieten ta oan &#39;e kassaside','These widget areas are used to add trust symbols and trust badges on the checkout page.' => 'Dizze widgetgebieten wurde brûkt om fertrouwensymboalen en fertrouwenbadges ta te foegjen op &#39;e kassaside.','Display checkout sidebar widgets only when viewing the last checkout step on mobile devices when using multi-step checkout layout' => 'Toan widgets foar de sydbalke fan &#39;e kassa allinich by it besjen fan&#39; e lêste ôfrekenstap op mobile apparaten by it brûken fan multi-stap checkout-yndieling','Enable integrated coupon code section' => 'Yntegreare coupon code seksje ynskeakelje','Only applicable if use of coupon codes are enabled in the WooCommerce settings.' => 'Allinnich fan tapassing as gebrûk fan kûponkoades ynskeakele binne yn &#39;e WooCommerce-ynstellingen.','Display the coupon codes section title' => 'Toan de titel fan de coupon koades seksje','Only applicable when coupon code is displayed as a separate section on the checkout or cart pages.' => 'Allinnich fan tapassing as coupon koade wurdt werjûn as in aparte seksje op de kassa of cart siden.','Select position where to display the coupon codes section on the checkout page.' => 'Selektearje posysje wêr&#39;t de coupon koades seksje op de kassa side te werjaan.','Before the checkout steps' => 'Foardat de kassa stappen','As a substep before payment methods' => 'As substap foar betelling metoaden','As a substep after payment methods' => 'As substap nei betelling metoaden','Select style of the "apply coupon" button. Only applicable when the coupon code section is displayed "Before the checkout steps" on the checkout page, or "Before the cart items section" on the cart page.' => 'Selektearje styl fan &#39;e knop &quot;kûpon tapasse&quot;. Allinnich fan tapassing as de seksje couponkoade wurdt werjûn &quot;Foar de kassa-stappen&quot; op &#39;e kassa-side, of &quot;Foar de seksje fan wein items&quot; op&#39; e cart-side.','Default button style' => 'Standert knop styl','"Add" link button' => '&quot;Tafoegje&quot; keppeling knop','Checkout fields' => 'Checkout fjilden','Optional fields' => 'Opsjonele fjilden','Hide optional fields behind a link button' => 'Ferbergje opsjonele fjilden efter in keppeling knop','It is recommended to keep this option checked to reduce the number of open input fields, <a href="https://baymard.com/blog/checkout-flow-average-form-fields#1-address-line-2--company-name-can-safely-be-collapsed-behind-a-link" target="_blank">read the research</a>.' => 'It is oan te rieden om dizze opsje ynskeakele te hâlden om it oantal iepen ynfierfjilden te ferminderjen, <a href="https://baymard.com/blog/checkout-flow-average-form-fields#1-address-line-2--company-name-can-safely-be-collapsed-behind-a-link" target="_blank">lês it ûndersyk</a> .','Do not hide "Address line 2" fields behind a link button' => 'Ferbergje &quot;Adresrigel 2&quot; fjilden net efter in keppeling knop','Recommended only when most customers actually need the "Address line 2" field, or when getting the right shipping address is crucial (ie. if delivering food and other perishable products).' => 'Allinich oanrikkemandearre as de measte klanten it fjild &quot;Adresline 2&quot; feitlik nedich binne, of as it krúsjaal is om it juste ferstjoeradres te krijen (dus as it leverjen fan iten en oare bederflike produkten).','Display the "Add" link buttons in lowercase' => 'Lit de &quot;Tafoegje&quot; keppeling knoppen yn lytse letters','Make the labels of optional field "Add" link button as <code>lowercase</code> (ie. "Add phone number" instead of "Add Phone Number"). This option also affects the link buttons for coupon code fields.' => 'Meitsje de labels fan opsjoneel fjild &quot;Tafoegje&quot; keppeling knop as <code>lowercase</code> (dws &quot;Tafoegje telefoannûmer&quot; ynstee fan &quot;Tafoegje telefoannûmer&quot;). Dizze opsje hat ek ynfloed op de keppeling knoppen foar coupon code fjilden.','Billing address' => 'Billing adres','Select position where to display the billing address section on the checkout page.' => 'Selektearje posysje wêr&#39;t it faktueradres seksje op &#39;e kassa-side te werjaan.','As a step before shipping' => 'As stap foar it ferstjoeren','As a sub-step before the shipping address section' => 'As sub-stap foar de seksje fan ferstjoeradres','As a sub-step after the shipping address section' => 'As sub-stap nei it ferstjoeradres seksje','As a step after shipping' => 'As stap nei skipfeart','As a sub-step before the payment section' => 'As sub-stap foar de betelling seksje','Force billing and shipping addresses to the same (single section)' => 'Tsjinje faktuer- en ferstjoeradressen nei itselde (ien seksje)','Checkbox for "Same as shipping/billing address" checked by default' => 'It karfakje foar &quot;Itselde as ferstjoerings-/faktureadres&quot; is standert kontrolearre','The checkbox "Same as shiping address" will start as checked by default when the shipping address section is displayed first. <br>The checkbox "Same as billing address" will start as checked by default when the billing address section is displayed first. <br> It is recommended to leave this option checked as to significantly reduce the number of open input fields at checkout, <a href="https://baymard.com/blog/checkout-flow-average-form-fields#3-default-billing--shipping-and-hide-the-fields-entirely" target="_blank">read the research</a>.' => 'It karfakje &quot;Itselde as ferstjoeradres&quot; sil begjinne as standert selektearre as de seksje ferstjoeradres earst wurdt werjûn.<br> It karfakje &quot;Itselde as faktueradres&quot; sil begjinne as standert selektearre as de faktueradres seksje earst werjûn wurdt.<br> It is oan te rieden om dizze opsje ynskeakele te litten om it oantal iepen ynfierfjilden by kassa signifikant te ferminderjen, <a href="https://baymard.com/blog/checkout-flow-average-form-fields#3-default-billing--shipping-and-hide-the-fields-entirely" target="_blank">lês it ûndersyk</a> .','Highlight the billing address section in the checkout form' => 'Markearje it faktueradres seksje yn it kassaformulier','Shipping address' => 'Shipping adres','Highlight the shipping address section in the checkout form' => 'Markearje de seksje fan ferstjoeradres yn it kassaformulier','Shipping methods' => 'Shipping metoaden','Choose in which position to display the shipping methods section.' => 'Kies yn hokker posysje de seksje ferstjoermetoaden werjaan.','Before shipping address' => 'Foardat skipfeart adres','After shipping address' => 'Nei ferstjoering adres','Prevent automatic selection of the first shipping method' => 'Foarkom automatyske seleksje fan de earste skipfeart metoade','When enabled, the first shipping method available will not be automatically selected when no other shipping method was previously selected for each shipping package. <br>This option will be automatically enabled if the option for clearing the selected shipping method is enabled for the Local Pickup feature.' => 'As it ynskeakele is, sil de earste beskikbere ferstjoermetoade net automatysk selektearre wurde as gjin oare ferstjoermetoade earder selektearre is foar elk ferstjoerpakket.<br> Dizze opsje sil automatysk ynskeakele wurde as de opsje foar it wiskjen fan de selekteare ferstjoermetoade ynskeakele is foar de funksje Local Pickup.','Local pickup' => 'Lokale pickup','Removes shipping address section when a local pickup shipping method is selected.' => 'Ferwideret seksje fan ferstjoeradres as in pleatslike ferstjoermetoade foar opheljen is selektearre.','Replaces the shipping address with the pickup point location when a local pickup shipping method is selected.' => 'Ferfangt it ferstjoeradres mei de lokaasje fan it opheljenpunt as in pleatslike ferstjoermetoade foar opheljen wurdt selektearre.','Show option to clear shipping methods in the pickup location substep' => 'Toan opsje om ferstjoermetoaden te wiskjen yn &#39;e substap foar opheljenlokaasje','Show a link button on the pickup location substep to clear the chosen shipping methods. This can be used to allow showing the shipping address section again if a local pickup method was previously selected.' => 'Toan in keppeling knop op de pickup lokaasje substap te wiskjen de keazen ferstjoermetoaden. Dit kin brûkt wurde om it werjaan fan &#39;e seksje fan ferstjoeradres wer te litten as in pleatslike oppakmetoade earder selektearre is.','Choose which address to save as the shipping address for local pickup orders.' => 'Kies hokker adres te bewarjen as it ferstjoeradres foar pleatslike pickup oarders.','Save the selected pickup location' => 'Bewarje de selektearre pickup lokaasje','Save same as the billing address' => 'Bewarje itselde as it faktureadres','Do not save any shipping address' => 'Bewarje gjin ferstjoeradres','Company name field for shipping address' => 'Bedriuwsnammefjild foar ferstjoeradres','Change visibility for the company name field for the shipping address section on the checkout form.' => 'Feroarje sichtberens foar it bedriuwsnammefjild foar de seksje ferstjoeradres op it kassaformulier.','If field is set as "optional", which is the default visibility state, no changes will be applied to let other plugins apply any changes they need.' => 'As fjild is ynsteld as &quot;opsjoneel&quot;, dat is de standert sichtberens tastân, gjin wizigings wurde tapast te litten oare plugins tapasse alle feroarings dy&#39;t se nedich hawwe.','Hidden (remove field)' => 'Ferburgen (fjild fuortsmite)','Optional' => 'Fakultatyf','Required' => 'Required','Add shipping phone field to the checkout form.' => 'Foegje ferstjoertelefonfjild ta oan it kassaformulier.','Choose in which step to display the shipping phone field.' => 'Kies yn hokker stap it ferstjoertelefoanfjild werjaan sil.','Contact step' => 'Kontakt stap','Billing phone' => 'Billing telefoan','Add billing phone field to the checkout form.' => 'Foegje fakturearring tillefoanfjild ta oan it kassaformulier.','Choose in which step to display the billing phone field.' => 'Kies yn hokker stap om it faktuertillefoanfjild wer te jaan.','Enable international phone number format and validation for phone fields' => 'Ynskeakelje ynternasjonaal telefoannûmer opmaak en falidaasje foar telefoan fjilden','Format and validate phone numbers according to each country.' => 'Opmaak en falidearje telefoannûmers neffens elk lân.','Enable phone number validation based on country rules' => 'Ynskeakelje telefoannûmer falidaasje basearre op lân regels','When disabled, the phone field validation will not check if country or area codes are valid for the country.' => 'As útskeakele, sil de falidaasje fan it telefoanfjild net kontrolearje oft lân- of gebietskoades jildich binne foar it lân.','Only show allowed countries for shipping or billing' => 'Lit allinich tastien lannen sjen foar ferstjoering of fakturearring','When enabled, only the countries allowed for shipping will be available in the shipping phone field, and only countries allowed for billing will be available for the billing phone field.' => 'As it ynskeakele is, sille allinich de lannen dy&#39;t tastien binne foar ferstjoering beskikber wêze yn it ferstjoertelefoanfjild, en allinich lannen tastien foar fakturearring sille beskikber wêze foar it fjild foar fakturearring.','Show country code beside the flag' => 'Lit lânkoade neist de flagge sjen','Show an example of a valid phone number inside phone fields' => 'Lit in foarbyld sjen fan in jildich telefoannûmer yn telefoanfjilden','Do not change placeholders' => 'Feroarje plakhâlders net','Show if not defined' => 'Lit sjen as net definiearre','Always show' => 'Altyd sjen litte','Order notes' => 'Oantekeningen bestelle','Define the visibility of the additional order notes field.' => 'Definiearje de sichtberens fan it fjild foar ekstra oardernotysjes.','Gift options' => 'Gift opsjes','Display gift message and other gift options at the checkout page' => 'Lit kado-berjocht en oare kado-opsjes sjen op &#39;e kassapagina','Allow customers to add a gift message and other gift related options to the order.' => 'Lit klanten in kadoberjocht en oare kado-relatearre opsjes tafoegje oan &#39;e bestelling.','Display the gift message fields always expanded' => 'Toan de kado berjocht fjilden altyd útwreide','Display the gift message as part of the order details table instead of a separate section' => 'Lit it kado-berjocht sjen as ûnderdiel fan &#39;e tabel foar bestellingsdetails ynstee fan in aparte seksje','This option affects the order confirmation page (thank you page) and order details on account pages, emails and packing slips.' => 'Dizze opsje hat ynfloed op de side foar befêstiging fan bestelling (betankeside) en besteldetails op akkountsiden, e-mails en pakslips.','Account matching' => 'Account matching','Enable the account matching feature' => 'Aktivearje de akkount oerienkommende funksje','Associate the guest customer\'s orders with their existing account when an account already exists with the customer\'s contact details.' => 'Assosiearje de oarders fan de gastklant mei har besteande akkount as der al in akkount bestiet mei de kontaktgegevens fan de klant.','Display message when an account exists with the email address provided' => 'Berjocht werjaan as der in akkount bestiet mei it opjûne e-mailadres','Replaces the account creation fields with a notification and option to log in. In some contexts, it might be recommended to leave this option disabled to protect the privacy of customers.' => 'Ferfangt de fjilden foar oanmeitsjen fan akkounts mei in notifikaasje en opsje om yn te loggen. Yn guon konteksten is it miskien oan te rieden om dizze opsje útskeakele te litten om de privacy fan klanten te beskermjen.','Dashboard' => 'Dashboard','Integrations' => 'Yntegraasjes','No integrations available at the moment on this section. The options related to each plugin will only appear here if that plugin is activated.' => 'Gjin yntegraasjes beskikber op it stuit op dizze seksje. De opsjes relatearre oan elke plugin sille hjir allinich ferskine as dy plugin aktivearre is.','License keys' => 'Lisinsje kaaien','No license keys options available at the moment on this section. The options related to each plugin or add-on will appear here when that plugin is activated.' => 'Gjin opsjes foar lisinsjekaaien beskikber op it stuit op dizze seksje. De opsjes relatearre oan elke plugin of tafoeging sille hjir ferskine as dat plugin is aktivearre.','Visit our website for more information about our plugins and add-ons.' => 'Besykje ús webside foar mear ynformaasje oer ús plugins en tafoegings.','Order pay page' => 'Betel betelje side','Order pay' => 'Bestelle betelje','Enable order pay page optimizations' => 'Ynskeakelje oarder betelje side optimizations','Changes the layout of order pay page for existing orders pending payment from the customer.' => 'Feroaret de yndieling fan oarder beteljen side foar besteande oarders yn ôfwachting fan betelling fan de klant.','Add widget areas to the order pay page' => 'Foegje widgetgebieten ta oan &#39;e oarder beteljen side','These widget areas are used to add trust symbols and trust badges on the order pay page.' => 'Dizze widgetgebieten wurde brûkt om fertrouwensymboalen en fertrouwenstekens ta te foegjen op &#39;e side foar bestelling beteljen.','Thank you page & order details layout' => 'Tankewol side &amp; oarder details layout','Order details optimizations' => 'Order details optimizations','Enable thank you page and order details optimizations' => 'Aktivearje tankje side en optimisaasjes foar besteldetails','Changes the layout of order details on the thank you page and account pages.' => 'Feroaret de yndieling fan bestellingsdetails op &#39;e tankside en akkount siden.','Enable order details customizations on email notifications' => 'Oanpassingen fan bestellingsdetails ynskeakelje op e-postnotifikaasjes','Display new sections and change order of sections on email notifications. Styles of order details on email notifications remain unchanged.' => 'Toan nije seksjes en feroarje de folchoarder fan seksjes op e-postnotifikaasjes. Stilen fan bestellingsdetails op e-postnotifikaasjes bliuwe net feroare.','Thank you page' => 'Tankewol side','These options affect the thank you page, also known as order received or order confirmation pages.' => 'Dizze opsjes beynfloedzje de tankside, ek wol bekend as siden foar ûntfongen bestelling of befêstiging fan bestelling.','Order details layout' => 'Bestelle details yndieling','Display the order details with wide layout on the thank you page' => 'Toan de bestellingsdetails mei brede yndieling op &#39;e tankside','Add widget areas to the thank you page' => 'Foegje widgetgebieten ta oan &#39;e tankside','These widget areas are used to add trust symbols and trust badges on the thank you page.' => 'Dizze widgetgebieten wurde brûkt om fertrouwensymboalen en fertrouwenbadges ta te foegjen op &#39;e tankside.','These options affect the thank you page , view order details on account pages and on email notifications.' => 'Dizze opsjes beynfloedzje de tankside, besjoch bestellingsdetails op akkountsiden en op e-postnotifikaasjes.','Order actions' => 'Bestelle aksjes','Choose in which position to display the order actions.' => 'Kies yn hokker posysje de folchoarderaksjes werjûn wurde.','Inside the order overview' => 'Binnen it oarder oersjoch','After the order overview' => 'Nei de oarder oersjoch','After order sections' => 'Nei oarder seksjes','Order status' => 'Order status','Display the order status progress bar' => 'Lit de foarútgongsbalke fan &#39;e oarderstatus sjen','Choose in which position to display the section.' => 'Kies yn hokker posysje de seksje werjaan sil.','After the order overview and payment instructions' => 'Nei de oarder oersjoch en betelling ynstruksjes','Before the order items section' => 'Foardat de bestelling items seksje','Inside the order items section' => 'Binnen de seksje oarder items','After the order items section' => 'Nei de bestelling items seksje','On the sidebar' => 'Op de sydbalke','Order downloads' => 'Bestelle downloads','Gift message' => 'Gift berjocht','Tools' => 'Tools','Troubleshooting' => 'Troubleshooting','Debug options' => 'Debug opsjes','Debug mode' => 'Debug modus','Using debug mode affects the website performance. Only use this option while troubleshooting.' => 'It brûken fan debugmodus beynfloedet de prestaasjes fan &#39;e webside. Brûk dizze opsje allinich by it oplossen fan problemen.','Load unminified assets' => 'Laad unminified aktiva','Enhanced select fields' => 'Ferbettere selektearje fjilden','Replace <code>select2</code> dropdown components with <code>TomSelect</code>' => 'Ferfange <code>select2</code> dropdown-komponinten mei <code>TomSelect</code>','TomSelect is a simpler dropdown selection component which is less prone to errors than Select2, while offering the same features that are actually used on WooCommerce checkout pages.' => 'TomSelect is in ienfâldiger dropdown-seleksjekomponint dy&#39;t minder gefoelich is foar flaters dan Select2, wylst se deselde funksjes oanbiede dy&#39;t eins wurde brûkt op WooCommerce kassasiden.','Fix automatic zoom-in on form fields' => 'Fix automatysk ynzoomen op formulierfjilden','Set <code>font-size</code> inside form fields to 16px' => 'Stel <code>font-size</code> yn formulierfjilden yn op 16px','When the font size inside form fields is smaller than 16px, Safari and other browsers might automatically zoom in on mobile devices to make the text easier to read. When this option is enabled, it will set the font size for inside the form fields to 16px on pages optimized by Fluid Checkout to avoid it zooming in.' => 'As de lettertypegrutte binnen formulierfjilden lytser is dan 16px, kinne Safari en oare browsers automatysk ynzoome op mobile apparaten om de tekst makliker te lêzen. As dizze opsje ynskeakele is, sil it de lettertypegrutte foar binnen de formulierfjilden ynstelle op 16px op siden optimalisearre troch Fluid Checkout om te foarkommen dat it ynzoomt.','The shipping destination is always set to "Default to customer shipping address" when Fluid Checkout is activated. Customers can still provide different shipping and billing addresses during checkout, an option for setting the default billing address to be the same as the shipping address is available at WooCommerce > Settings > Fluid Checkout.' => 'De skipfeartbestimming is altyd ynsteld op &quot;Standert foar ferstjoeradres fan klant&quot; as Fluid Checkout is aktivearre. Klanten kinne noch ferskate ferstjoerings- en fakturearadressen leverje tidens de kassa, in opsje foar it ynstellen fan it standert faktureadres om itselde te wêzen as it ferstjoeradres is beskikber by WooCommerce&gt; Ynstellings&gt; Fluid Checkout.','Fluid Checkout' => 'Fluid Checkout','Settings' => 'Ynstellings','Support' => 'Stypje','<a target="_blank" href="%s">Upgrade to PRO</a> to unlock more options.' => '<a target="_blank" href="%s">Upgrade nei PRO</a> om mear opsjes te ûntsluten.','(PRO)' => '(PRO)','(experimental)' => '(eksperiminteel)','This is an experimental feature and may not work as expected with all themes and plugins. Use it with caution.' => 'Dit is in eksperimintele funksje en wurket miskien net lykas ferwachte mei alle tema&#39;s en plugins. Brûk it mei foarsichtigens.','Confirm' => 'Befêstigje','Verify Phone Number' => 'Ferifiearje telefoannûmer','Please verify your phone number.' => 'Ferifiearje asjebleaft jo telefoannûmer.','The Bluehost Plugin' => 'De Bluehost Plugin','Custom fields' => 'Oanpaste fjilden','Enable custom shipping email field' => 'Oanpaste e-postfjild foar ferstjoering ynskeakelje','When enabled, the shipping email field from the Bluehost plugin will be added to the checkout form.' => 'As it ynskeakele is, sil it ferstjoere-e-postfjild fan &#39;e Bluehost-plugin wurde tafoege oan it kassaformulier.','Captcha Pro by BestWebSoft' => 'Captcha Pro troch BestWebSoft','Captcha position' => 'Captcha posysje','Define the position to display the captcha section. Some positions might not work depending on the captcha type chosen.' => 'Definiearje de posysje om de captcha-seksje wer te jaan. Guon posysjes wurkje miskien net ôfhinklik fan it keazen captcha-type.','Selecting a pickup point is required before proceeding.' => 'It selektearjen fan in opheljenpunt is ferplichte foardat jo trochgean.','Pickup point' => 'Pickup punt','Pickup point not selected yet.' => 'Opheljen punt noch net selektearre.','Pickup point:' => 'Opfangpunt:','Mailchimp for WooCommerce' => 'Mailchimp foar WooCommerce','Subscribe checkbox' => 'Abonnearje karfakje','Override the position for the subscribe checkbox on the checkout page and always display it on the contact step' => 'Oerskriuwe de posysje foar it karfakje foar abonnemint op &#39;e kassapagina en lit it altyd werjaan op&#39; e kontaktstap','Before Shipping Address' => 'Foardat Shipping Adres','(originally "%s")' => '(oarspronklik &quot;%s&quot;)','After Shipping Address' => 'Nei Shipping Adres','Selecting a collection point is required when shipping with FermoPoint.' => 'It selektearjen fan in sammelpunt is ferplichte by ferstjoeren mei FermoPoint.','If checked informs typos in email to users. (This feature has been disabled because Fluid Checkout offers the feature. Changes to this option will not take effect)' => 'As selekteare ynformearret typfouten yn e-post oan brûkers. (Dizze funksje is útskeakele om&#39;t Fluid Checkout de funksje biedt. Feroarings oan dizze opsje sille net fan krêft wurde)','Enable Mail Check: (disabled feature)' => 'Postkontrôle ynskeakelje: (funksje útskeakele)','Carrier:' => 'Ferfierder:','Sendinblue - WooCommerce Email Marketing' => 'Sendinblue - WooCommerce E-postmarketing','Sign up checkbox position' => 'Oanmelde checkbox posysje','Move the sign up checkbox to the contact step' => 'Ferpleats it karfakje foar oanmelding nei de kontaktstap','When enabled, the checkbox will be moved to the contact step independently of the display location defined in the Sendinblue plugin settings.' => 'As it ynskeakele is, sil it karfakje ferpleatst wurde nei de kontaktstap ûnôfhinklik fan &#39;e werjeftelokaasje definieare yn&#39; e Sendinblue-pluginynstellingen.','Theme Betheme' => 'Tema Betheme','Checkout progress' => 'Checkout foarútgong','Output the checkout steps section from Betheme on the checkout, cart and order received pages.' => 'Utfiere de seksje fan &#39;e kassa-stappen fan Betheme op&#39; e kassa, karre en bestelle ûntfongen siden.','Theme Fennik' => 'Tema Fennik','Breadcrumbs' => 'Broodkruimels','Output the breadcrumbs section from the Fennik theme when using Fluid Checkout header and footer.' => 'Utfiere de breadcrumbs-seksje út it Fennik-tema by it brûken fan Fluid Checkout-kop- en fuottekst.','Theme Go' => 'Tema gean','My account layout' => 'Myn account yndieling','Enable wide layout on "My account" page.' => 'Wide yndieling ynskeakelje op &#39;Myn akkount&#39; side.','Theme Impreza' => 'Tema Impreza','Header' => 'Koptekst','Spacing for site header at the checkout page (in pixels)' => 'Spaasje foar sidekoptekst by de kassaside (yn piksels)','Only applicable when using the Impreza theme header at the checkout page.' => 'Allinich fan tapassing by it brûken fan de Impreza-temakoptekst by de kassaside.','Theme Kapee' => 'Tema Kapee','Output the checkout steps section from the Kapee theme on the checkout, cart and order received pages.' => 'Utfiere de seksje fan &#39;e kassa-stappen út it Kapee-tema op&#39; e kassa, karre en bestelle ûntfongen siden.','Theme Porto' => 'Tema Porto','Output the checkout steps section from the Porto theme on the checkout, cart and order received pages.' => 'Utfiere de seksje fan &#39;e kassa-stappen út it Porto-tema op&#39; e kassa, karre en bestelle ûntfongen siden.','Theme Pressmart' => 'Tema Pressmart','Output the checkout steps section from the Pressmart theme on the checkout, cart and order received pages.' => 'Utfiere de seksje fan &#39;e kassa-stappen út it Pressmart-tema op&#39; e kassa, karre en ûntfongen siden.','Theme The Gem' => 'Tema De Gem','Output the checkout steps section from The Gem theme when using Fluid Checkout header and footer.' => 'Utfiere de seksje fan &#39;e kassa-stappen út The Gem-tema by it brûken fan Fluid Checkout-kop- en fuottekst.','Theme Woodmart' => 'Tema Woodmart','Output the checkout steps section from the Woodmart theme when using Fluid Checkout header and footer.' => 'Utfiere de seksje fan &#39;e kontrôlestappen út it Woodmart-tema by it brûken fan Fluid Checkout-kop- en fuottekst.','Checkout options' => 'Checkout opsjes','Disable the theme checkout options' => 'Skeakelje de opsjes foar ôfrekken fan tema&#39;s','The options display product image, quantity field, remove button and link to product page added by the theme are disabled by default.' => 'De opsjes werjaan produktôfbylding, kwantiteitfjild, knop fuortsmite en keppeling nei produktside tafoege troch it tema binne standert útskeakele.','Theme Atomion' => 'Tema Atomion','Order progress' => 'Order foarútgong','Display order progress from the theme' => 'Toan oarder foarútgong fan it tema','Display the form field labels visible on the page' => 'Toan de formulierfjildlabels sichtber op &#39;e side','It is recommended to keep this option enabled for a better user experience.' => 'It is oan te rieden om dizze opsje ynskeakele te hâlden foar in bettere brûkersûnderfining.','Theme ZK Nito' => 'Tema ZK Nito','Add extra fields to the checkout form' => 'Foegje ekstra fjilden ta oan it kassaformulier','Adds an extra shipping email and shipping phone field to the shipping address section.' => 'Foeget in ekstra ferstjoere-e-post en ferstjoertelefoanfjild ta oan it seksje fan ferstjoeradres.','Go to the home page' => 'Gean nei de thússide','Skip to content' => 'Gean nei ynhâld','Create an account' => 'Meitsje in akkount','Log in to your account' => 'Oanmelde by jo akkount','Already have an account?' => 'Al in akkount?','Logged in as %1$s. <a href="%2$s">Log out</a>' => 'Oanmelde as %1$s. <a href="%2$s">Log út</a>','Your order has a total amount due of %s. No further payment is needed.' => 'Jo bestelling hat in totaal ferskuldige bedrach fan %s. Gjin fierdere betelling is nedich.','Close and continue with checkout' => 'Slút en fierder mei kassa','Continue' => 'Trochgean','Parcel terminal' => 'Pakket terminal','<p>This widget has been replaced by Fluid Checkout. </p><p>When using Fluid Checkout, the checkout page needs to use the original WooCommerce shortcode <code>[woocommerce_checkout]</code> to work properly.</p><p>For more information, visit the Fluid Checkout documentation.</p>' => '<p>Dizze widget is ferfongen troch Fluid Checkout.</p><p> By it brûken fan Fluid Checkout moat de kassaside de orizjinele WooCommerce shortcode <code>[woocommerce_checkout]</code> brûke om goed te wurkjen.</p><p> Foar mear ynformaasje, besykje de Fluid Checkout dokumintaasje.</p>','Theme The7' => 'Tema 7','Additional header sections' => 'Oanfoljende kopteksten','Output additional header sections if enabled in the theme settings.' => 'Utfiere ekstra koptekstseksjes as ynskeakele is yn &#39;e tema-ynstellingen.','More information' => 'Mear ynformaasje','Pick a Locker' => 'Kies in locker','Page template' => 'Sidesjabloan','Use `Order confirmation` page template for block-based themes' => 'Brûk de sidesjabloan `Bestellingbefêstiging` foar blokbasearre tema&#39;s','Only applies when using a block-based theme.' => 'Allinnich jildt by it brûken fan in blok-basearre tema.','WooCommerce Stripe Gateway' => 'WooCommerce Stripe Gateway','Payment form' => 'Betellingsformulier','Apply styles to the Stripe payment form fields' => 'Stilen tapasse op &#39;e fjilden fan it Stripe-betellingsformulier','When enabled, Fluid Checkout will apply styles optimized for compatibility with the plugin. You may want to disable this if you are using custom styles for the Stripe payment form fields.' => 'As it ynskeakele is, sil Fluid Checkout stilen tapasse dy&#39;t optimalisearre binne foar kompatibiliteit mei de plugin. Jo kinne dit útskeakelje as jo oanpaste stilen brûke foar de fjilden fan it Stripe-betellingsformulier.','Theme Nyture' => 'Tema Nyture','Output the checkout steps section from the Nyture theme when using Fluid Checkout.' => 'Jou de seksje oer de kassa út fan it Nyture-tema út by it brûken fan Fluid Checkout.','Maybe be forced as "required" if the billing address section is displayed after the shipping address section, and the billing phone field is set as "required. This is needed to ensure the shipping address can be copied to the billing address when that option is checked.' => 'Miskien twongen wurde as &quot;ferplicht&quot; as it fakturearadresdiel werjûn wurdt nei it ferstjoeradresdiel, en it fjild foar faktureartelefoan is ynsteld as &quot;ferplicht&quot;. Dit is nedich om te soargjen dat it ferstjoeradres nei it fakturearadres kopiearre wurde kin as dy opsje oankrúst is.','Maybe be forced as "required" if the billing address section is displayed after the billing address section, and the billing phone field is set as "required. This is needed to ensure the billing address can be copied to the billing address when that option is checked.' => 'Miskien twongen wurde as &quot;ferplicht&quot; as it fakturearadresdiel nei it fakturearadresdiel werjûn wurdt, en it fjild foar faktureartelefoan is ynsteld as &quot;ferplicht&quot;. Dit is nedich om te soargjen dat it fakturearadres nei it fakturearadres kopiearre wurde kin as dy opsje oankrúst is.','Allows customers to make payments for orders that are either created manually by the store admin or not completed during checkout.' => 'Lit klanten betellingen dwaan foar oarders dy&#39;t of mei de hân oanmakke binne troch de winkelbehearder of net foltôge binne by it beteljen.','The plugin WooCommerce Checkout Manager by Quadlayers is not compatible with Fluid Checkout' => 'De plugin WooCommerce Checkout Manager fan Quadlayers is net kompatibel mei Fluid Checkout','Company name field for billing address' => 'Bedriuwsnammefjild foar fakturearadres','Change visibility for the company name field for the billing address section on the checkout form.' => 'Wizigje de sichtberens foar it fjild foar bedriuwsnamme foar it fakturearadresdiel op it kassaformulier.','Theme Bookshelf' => 'Tema Boekplank','Output the checkout steps section from the Bookshelf theme when using Fluid Checkout.' => 'Jou de seksje mei stappen foar it beteljen út fan it Bookshelf-tema út by it brûken fan Fluid Checkout.','Account password' => 'Wachtwurd fan it akkount','An account will be created with the information provided at checkout when completing the order.' => 'Der wurdt in akkount oanmakke mei de ynformaasje dy&#39;t by it beteljen fan &#39;e bestelling opjûn is.','Choose the style of the progress bar.' => 'Kies de styl fan &#39;e foarútgongsbalke.','Bars' => 'Bars','Theme Ireca' => 'Tema Ireca','WooCommerce page layout' => 'WooCommerce-side-yndieling','Force wide layout on WooCommerce pages' => 'Forsearje brede yndieling op WooCommerce-pagina&#39;s','This ensures the content section is not too narrow on WooCommerce pages including checkout, cart, order received, order pay and account pages.' => 'Dit soarget derfoar dat de ynhâldsseksje net te smel is op WooCommerce-siden, ynklusyf de siden foar kassa, winkelwein, ûntfongen bestelling, beteljen fan bestelling en akkount.','Button label for applying coupon codesApply' => 'Tapasse','Checkout step titleContact' => 'Kontakt','Checkout step titleShipping' => 'Skipfeart','Checkout step titleBilling' => 'Billing','Checkout step titlePayment' => 'Betelling','Checkout substep change link labelChange' => 'Feroaring','Checkout substep save link labelSave changes' => 'Bewarje feroarings','Substep review textNone.' => 'Gjin.','Substep review field format%1$s' => '%1$s','Substep review field format: with label%2$s: %1$s' => '%2$s: %1$s','Image uploader.No image selected.' => 'Gjin ôfbylding selektearre.','Settings sectionCart' => 'Cart','Settings sectionOrder pay' => 'Betel betelje','Settings sectionThank you' => 'Dankewol','Settings section titleIntegrations' => 'Yntegraasjes','Settings section titleLicense keys' => 'Lisinsje kaaien','Captcha positionBefore place order section' => 'Foardat plak oarder seksje','Captcha positionBefore place order button' => 'Foardat plak bestelling knop','No shipping method chosen label for the order summary--' => '--','Close button aria-labelClose' => 'Slute','Log in link label at checkout contact stepLog in' => 'Oanmelde','Log in separator label at for when guest checkout is disabledOr continue below' => 'Of trochgean hjirûnder','Log in separator label at for when guest checkout is disabledOr continue as a guest' => 'Of trochgean as gast','Clear image selection on admin pages.Remove image' => 'Ofbylding fuortsmite',] ];